  Goa2 ti7 hit e5 kau3-hoe7 choe3 sin5-hu7 25 ni5, than2-peh8 kong2, goa2 thiaN3 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2 kau3-hoe7, i ia7 thiaN3 goa2. Goa2 ui7-tioh8 goa2 e5 kau3-hoe7 kam-goan7 lau5-chhut goa2 sou2 u7 e5 mui2 chit8-tih huih, ia7 kam-goan7 hong7-hian3 chheng-poe7 e5 siN3-mia7 lai5 khok-tiong i e5 koan5-lek8 kap ui-giam5 ti7 choan5 Bi2-kok tai7-liok8, sim7-chi3 ti7 choan5 se3-kai3. Goa2 toa7 e5 ng3-bang7 chiu7-si7 kai2-pian3 Sin-kau3-tou5, chhoa7 in kui-ng3 ti7 goan2 e5 kau3-hoe7, in-ui7 goa2 u7 siu7 beng7-leng7, koh chiau3 an2-ni thoan5 kong2, tu5 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2 Kau3-hoe7 i2-goa7 bo5 kiu3-un, siang5-si5 goa2 na7 siuN7-tioh8 choe7-choe7 e5 Sin-kau3-tou5 beh sit-loh8 in e5 leng5-hun5, kam2-kak chin kho2-sioh. 
  Goa2 chhut-si3 kui2-ni5-au7, goan2 chiu7 poaN-khi3 chit8-e5 bo5 hak8-hau7 e5 sou2-chai7 khia7-khi2. Goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 choe3 goa2 thau5 chit8-e5 sian-siN, i ka3 goa2 thak8 e5 thau5 chit8-pun2 chheh chiu7-si7 Seng3-keng. Ti7 goa2 8, 9 he3 e5 si5, goa2 chiu7 eng7 chit8-chiong2 giau5-gi5 e5 sim-cheng5 lai5 thak8 Seng3-keng, goa2 e5 sim ia7 hou7 Siong7-te3 sui2 e5 Oe7 sou2 chhim-chiam3. Goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 u7 keng2 i sou2 ai3 goa2 thak8 e5 chiuN-chat, goa2 ia7 chin chu3-i3 ui7-tioh8 beh hiong2-siu7 thak8 Seng3-keng e5 khoai3-lok8, kui2-na7 pai2 ku7-choat8 chhut-khi3 goa7-bin7 kap soe3-han3 gin2-na2 saN-kap thit-tho5. U7 chit8-koa2 goa2 tek8-piat8 ai3 e5 chiuN-chat, goa2 chiu7 am3-ki3 oah8-liam7. 
  Chong2-si7 tui3 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 si2 liau2-au7, goan2 chhu3-nih hit-pun2 Seng3-keng soa3 bo5 khi3. Kiam2-chhai2 si7 hou7 sin5-hu7 theh8 khi3. TaN chit-pun2 Seng3-keng piN3-choe3 chit-e5 kou3-su7 it-chhe3 e5 kun-goan5. Chit-pun2 Seng3-keng ia7 si7 ti7 goa2 siau3-lian5 e5 si5, chio3 jip8 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5 e5 kng, kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, hit-e5 kng boe7-bat hoa-khi3. Hit e5 kng iau2-ku2 ti7-teh. Tit8 kau3 kin-na2-jit8, hit-pun2 kho2-ai3 e5 Seng3-keng eng7 Siong7-te3 e5 chu5-ai3, hou7 goa2 seng5-siu7 bo5-hoat-tou7 thang heng5-iong5 e5 khoai3-lok8, goa2 kam2-kak i2-keng tit-tioh8 kiu3-siok8, ti7 hit tiong-kan tit-tioh8 kng chio3, ji7-chhiaN2 oe7 thang ti7 chin-li2 e5 chheng-choaN5 lai5 lim-chiah8. 
  Chong2-si7 kiam2-chhai2 li2 beh tui3 goa2 an2-ni mng7: “Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 sin5-hu7 kiam2 m7-si7 m7 chun2 in e5 kau3-iu2 thak8 Seng3-keng mah?” Si7, pun2-lai5 si7 an2-ni. Chong2-si7 kam2-sia7 Chu2, kin-na2-jit8 e5 su7-sit8, chha-put-to choan5 se3-kai3 e5 Thian-chu2-kau3 long2 seng5-jin7 un2-chun2 lang5 thak8 Seng3-keng, ia7 ti7 chit8-koa2 sin3 Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 ka-teng5 tiong, li2 oe7 thang hoat-hian7 in u7 Seng3-keng. 
