  Peng5-iu2! Kin-na2-jit8 li2 na7 khi3 mng7 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2 kau3-tou5 khoaN3 in si7 m7-si7 siu7 hu2-kho2 lai5 thak8 Seng3-keng. In beh ka7 li2 kong2: “Si7, goan2 oe7-thang thak8.” Chong2-si7 koh mng7 kong2: “Lin2 u7 siu7 un2-chun2 lai5 koe2-soeh Seng3-keng a2-bo5?” In beh ka7 li2 kong2: “Boe7 eng7 tit.” Sin5-hu7 beng5-beng5 tui3 kau3-iu2 kong2, kau3-hoe7 ia7 beng5-beng5 tui3 sin5-hu7 kong2, in boe7 eng7-tit chiau3 in ka-ki7 e5 ti3-sek, ka-ki7 e5 liong5-sim lai5 koe2-soeh Seng3-keng tiong e5 jim7-ho5 chit8-ku3 oe7, ia7 na7 u7 lang5 koe2-soeh jim7-ho5 chit8-ku3, i pun2-sin chiu7 oe7 ham7-loh8 ti7 chit8-chiong2 kek8 pi-chham2 e5 choe7 tiong. Sin5-hu7 sit8-chai7 u7 tui3 kau3-iu2 kong2: “Siat-su2 li2 na7 siuN7 beh eng7 li2 ka-ki7 e5 ti3-sek lai5 koe2-soeh Seng3-keng, li2 chiu7 oe7 biat8-bong5. Seng3-keng si7 chit8-pun2 choe3 gui5-hiam2 e5 chheh. Li2 thang thak8, chong2-si7 choe3-ho2 m7-thang thak8, in-ui7 li2 boe7 oe7 li2-kai2.” 
  Chit-chiong2 ka3-si7 e5 kiat-ko2 si7 sim2-mih8 neh? Chit-e5 kiat-ko2 chiu7-si7 kong2, sui-jian5 sin5-hu7 kap kau3-iu2 long2 u7 chit8-pun2 Seng3-keng, in ia7 bo5 thak8. Ka3-su2 u7 chit8-pun2 chheh, li2 chai li2 pun2-sin boe7-thang li2-kai2, li2 kiam2 beh thak8 mah? Li2 kiam2 hiah-nih gong7, beh long7-hui3 li2 e5 si5-kan khi3 thak8 chit8-pun2 li2 ka-ki7 chai pun2-sin lian5 chit8-ku3 ia7 boe7 li2-kai2 e5 chheh mah? Peng5-iu2, che chiu7-si7 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2 kau3-hoe7 e5 su7-sit8. In u7 chin choe7 e5 Seng3-keng. Ti7 mui2 chit8-e5 sin5-hu7 kap Thian-chu2 kau3-iu2 e5 toh-teng2, li2 beh khoaN3-tioh8 Seng3-keng, chong2-si7 ti7 chit8-ban7 e5 sin5-hu7 tiong, bo5 chiuN7 nng7 e5 bat chiong Seng3-keng tui3 thau5 kau3 boe2 chu3-i3 thak8 chit8-pian3 koe3 e5. In long2 si7 chia thak8 kui2-phiN, hia thak8 kui2-phiN chiu7 soah khi3. 
