  Goa2 e5 choe3-toa7 e5 bok8-tek chiu7-si7 piaN3-to2 Bi2-kok Sin-kau3 e5 Bok8-su. Goa2 u7 tit-tioh8 chit8-pun2 chheh, kio3 choe3 “Seng3 Kau3-hu7”. Goa2 ui7-tioh8 beh chun2-pi7 tui3-khong3 Sin kau3-tou5, kap in toa7 kau-chian3, chiu7 mi5-jit8 eng7 chit-pun2 chheh kap Seng3-keng tui3-chiau3 lai5 gian2-kiu3. Goa2 an2-ni gian2-kiu3 si7 ui7-tioh8 beh kian-kou3 goa2 ti7 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2 kau3-hoe7 e5 sin3-giong2. 
  Chong2-si7 kam2-sia7 su3-hok e5 Siong7-te3, goa2 mui2-pai2 thak8 Seng3-keng e5 si5, u7 chit8-chiong2 sin5-pi3 e5 siaN tui3 goa2 kong2, “Li2 kiam2 bo5 khoaN3-chhut ti7 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2 kau3-hoe7, lin2 bo5 sun7-than3 Siong7-te3 sou2 ka3-si7 e5 oe7, chi2-u7 sun7-than3 lang5 e5 thoan5-thong2?” Ti7 am3-si5 chheng-cheng7 e5 si5, goa2 thiaN tioh8 hit e5 siaN-im chiu7 thi5-khau3 lau5 bak8-sai2, chong2-si7 hit-e5 siaN iu5-goan5 chhin-chhiuN7 lui5 e5 siaN teh hoan2-hok. Goa2 ai3 tiam3 ti7 Seng3 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2 kau3-hoe7 lai5 oah8, lai5 si2, sou2-i2 goa2 chiu7 ki5-to2 kiu5 Siong7-te3 hou7 chit-e5 siaN tiam7-khi3, chong2-si7 goa2 thiaN-kiN3 hit-e5 siaN-im iu5-goan5 na2 toa7-soaN. Tng goa2 thak8 I e5 Oe7 e5 si5, I siuN7 beh thau2-khui goa2 e5 so2-lian7, chong2-si7 goa2 bo5 ai3 goa2 e5 so2-lian7 siu7 thau2-khui. I toa3 I chin2-kiu3 e5 kng lai5 chiu7-kun7 goa2, chong2-si7 goa2 bo5 beh chiap-lap8 I. 
  Goa2 tui3 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 sin5-hu7 peng3 bo5 ok-kam2. Kiam2-chhai2 lin2 tiong-kan u7 lang5 beh siuN7 kong2, goa2 tui3 in u7 ok-kam2, an2-ni lin2 chiu7 chho3 lah. U7-si5 goa2 ui7-tioh8 in thi5-khau3, in-ui7 goa2 chai in tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 goa2 koe3-khi3 sou2 choe3 e5 chit8-iuN7, goa2 Chu2 saN ti2-khong3, si7 thang pi-siong kho2-lin5 e5 lang5. Siat-su2 lin2 tiong-kan u7 lang5 chiau3 goa2 sou2 kong2, kap goa2 tang5 chit8-iuN7 ti7 cheng-chat tiong, lin2 it-teng7 oe7 li2-kai2 choe3 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 sin5-hu7 si7 sim2-mih8 khoan2, lin2 ia7 it-teng7 beh ui7-tioh8 in ki5-to2. 
  Ti7 Bun5-li2-lek8 (Montreal) u7 chit8-keng oe7 thang iong5 un2 15000 lang5, chin sui2 e5 Thian-chu2 kau3-tng5. Goa2 koe3-khi3 siong5-siong5 ti7 hia kang2-to7. U7 chit8-jit8, Chu2-kau3 chhiaN2 goa2 kong2 “Chai7-sek-lu2 Ma2-li7-a”, goa2 chin hoaN-hi2 ka7 i tah-eng3. Goa2 tui3 hia e5 kau3-iu2 kong2-khi2 goa2 liah8 choe3 chin-sit8 e5 to7-li2, ia7 si7 sin5-hu7 sou2 sin3, ti7 kok sou2-chai7 sou2 thoan5 e5. E7-bin7 chiah-e5 chiu7-si7 goa2 sou2 thoan5 e5 to7-li2:------
  “Chhin-ai3 e5 peng5-iu2! Tng chit8 e5 lang5 poe7-poan7 i e5 kok-ong5, a2-si7 tui3 i e5 hong5-te3 hoan7-tioh8 chin toa7 e5 choe7 e5 si5, i kiam2 beh pun2-sun khi3 tui3 kok-ong5 kiu5 sia3-bian2 mah? Siat-su2 i u7 chit8 e5 chheng2-kiu5 beh tui3 kok-ong5 kong2, i kiam2 kaN2 eng7 chit8-e5 choe7-jin5 e5 sin-hun7 khi3 kau3 kok-ong5 e5 bin7-cheng5 kiu5 mah? Boe7 eng7-tit! Kok-ong5 tek-khak beh ka7 i khian3-chek, ka7 i heng5-hoat8. Na7 si7 an2-ni i tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 choe3? Choe3 ho2 i tioh8 khi3 chhoe7 kok-ong5 e5 peng5-iu2, a2-si7 i e5 koaN-oan5, u7-si5 tioh8 chhoe7 kok-ong5 e5 chi2-mai7 a2-si7 lau7-bu2 lai5 the3 i kong2-cheng5, ia7 tioh8 chiong i e5 chheng2-goan7 kia3 in theh8 khi3. In chiu7 khi3 the3 hit-e5 choe7-jin5 kiu5 cheng5, tui3 kok-ong5 kiu5 sia3-bian2, soah kok-ong5 e5 siu7-khi3. Na7 an2-ni choe3, kok-ong5 siong5-siong5 oe7 eng3-un2 chiah-e5 lang5 e5 chheng2-kiu5, chiu7 si7 pun2-lai5 i oe7 tui3 choe7-jin5 ku7-choat8 e5. 
  Goa2 koh kong2: “An2-ni, lan2 long2 si7 choe7-jin5, lan2 long2 ui5-poe7 hit-e5 ui2-tai7 koh u7 leng5-lek8 e5 ong5, ban7-ong5 e5 Ong5. Lan2 long2 tui3 i siN-khi2 hoan2-khong3 e5 bin7-bak8. Lan2 chiong I e5 lut8-hoat thun2-tah8 ti7 lan2 e5 kha-e7, I tek-khak tui3 lan2 hoat siu7-khi3. TaN kin-na2-jit8 lan2 oe7 thang choe3 sim2-mih8 neh? Lan2 kiam2 oe7-thang toa3-tioh8 chhiong-moa2 choe7-ok e5 chhiu2 khi3 chiu7-kun7 I mah? Boe7 eng7 tit. Chong2-si7 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, lan2 u7 lan2 e5 Ong5 Ia5-sou e5 lau7-bu2 Ma2-li7-a ti7 I e5 chiaN3-peng5, in-ui7 I si7 chit8-e5 iu2-hau3 e5 kiaN2, boe7 bat ku7-choat8 kho2-ai3 e5 lau7-bu2 sou2 kiu5 e5, sou2-i2 Ia5-sou tek-khak boe7-oe7 ku7-choat8 Ma2-li7-a e5 chheng2-kiu5. Tng I ti7 se3-kan e5 si5, I boe7-bat ku7-choat8 Ma2-li7-a sou2 the5-chhut e5 jim7-ho5 chheng2-goan7. I bo5-lun7 ti7 sim2-mih8 su7 long2 boe7 bat ku7-choat8 I e5 lau7-bu2. 
  Tng chit8-e5 lang5 oe7-thang in-ui7 tah-eng3 i e5 lau7-bu2 e5 sou2-ai3 lai5 hou7 lau7-bu2 hoaN-hi2 e5 si5, kiam2 beh tiau5-kou3-i3 m7-thiaN ti3-kau3 hou7 sou2 thiaN3 e5 lau7-bu2 siong-sim mah?” Goa2 koh kong2, “Ban7 ong5 e5 Ong5 Ia5-sou, put-tan3 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2, ia7 si7 Ma2-li7-a e5 kiaN2, I ia7 thiaN3 I e5 lau7-bu2. In-ui7 I ti7 se3-kan e5 si5, boe7-bat ku7-choat8 Ma2-li7-a sou2 kiu5 e5; I kin-na2-jit8 ia7 tek-khak boe7 ku7-choat8 i sou2 kiu5 e5. An2-ni lan2 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 cho3 neh? Ah! Lan2 boe7 thang toa3 lan2 e5 choe7 lai5 kau3 ui2-tai7 e5 Ong5 e5 bin7-cheng5. Lan2 tioh8 chiong lan2 e5 chheng2-goan7 toa3 kau3 Seng3-bu2 hia; i beh khi3 kau3 Ia5-sou e5 kha cheng5, Ia5-sou pun2-sin chiu7 si7 I e5 Siong7-te3, ia7 si7 i e5 kiaN2, i sou2 kiu5 e5, tek-khak beh tit-tioh8; i beh ui7-tioh8 lan2 kiu5 sia3-bian2, ia7 tek-khak oe7 tit-tioh8 seng5-chiu7. I beh ui7-tioh8 lan2 kiu5 Ki-tok e5 Ong5-kok, hou7 lan2 ti7 hia oe7 tit-tioh8 chit8-e5 sou2-chai7. I beh kiu5 Ia5-sou boe7 ki3-tit lin2 e5 koe3-sit, chiap-lap8 lin2 chin e5 hoe2-kai2, Ia5-sou ia7 beh chiong I e5 lau7-bu2 ui7-tioh8 li2 tui3 I kiu5 e5 siuN2-su3 li2.” 
  Goa2 e5 thiaN-chiong3 thiaN tioh8 u7 chit-chiong2 e5 tiong-po2, mi5-jit8 ti7 Ia5-sou e5 kha-cheng5 ui7-tioh8 in teh ki5-kiu5 e5 si5, in khoai3-lok8 kau3 lau5 bak8-sai2, in ia7 in-ui7 Ma2-li7-a oe7 the3 in kiu5, hou7 in e5 choe7 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2, kak-tit chin hoaN-hi2. 
  Hit-si5, goa2 siuN7 che put-tan3 si7 Ki-tok-kau3 iau3-kin2 e5 kau3-li2, ia7 si7 it-poaN sin3-tou5 tek-khak tioh8 chai e5 siong5-sek, sou2-i2 bo5 sim2-mih8 oe7 thang kap i pian7-pok e5. Kang2-to7 soah liau2-au7, Chu2-kau3 lai5 ka7 goa2 chiok-hok, koh ka7 goa2 soeh-sia7. I kong2 chit-phiN kang2-to7 tui3 ti7 Bun5-li2-lek (Montreal) u7 chin toa7 e5 li7-ek. 
  Ti7 hit-mi5, goa2 kui7-teh, theh8 Seng3-keng lai5, ia7 goa2 e5 sim moa2-moa2 u7 khoai3-lok8, in-ui7 hit cha2-khi2 goa2 sou2 thoan5 e5 si7 chit8-phiN chin ho2 e5 kang2-to7. Goa2 hian-khui Seng3-keng tui3 Ma2-thai3 12 chiuN 26 chat khi2 thak8 e7-bin7 chiah-e5 oe7. 
  “I iau2 tui3 cheng3-lang5 kong2-oe7 e5 si5, tu2-tng7 I e5 lau7-bu2 kap I e5 hiaN-ti7 ti7 goa7-bin7, ai3 beh kap I kong2-oe7. U7 lang5 ka7 I kong2, Li2 khoaN3, li2 e5 lau7-bu2 kap li2 e5 hiaN-ti7 khia7 ti7 goa7-bin7, ai3 beh kap li2 kong2-oe7. Chiu7 in3 hit e5 ka7 I kong2 e5 kong2, sim2-mih8 lang5 si7 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2? Sim2-mih8 lang5 si7 goa2 e5 hiaN-ti7 ah? Chiu7 chhun-chhiu2 ki2 I e5 hak8-seng kong2, Li2 khoaN3, goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 kap goa2 e5 hiaN-ti7. In-ui7 kiN3-na7 kiaN5 goa2 ti7 thiN-nih e5 Pe7 e5 chi2-i3 e5, chiu7-si7 goa2 e5 hiaN-ti7, chi2-be7 kap lau7-bu2.” (Ma2-thai3 12: 46-50) 
  Tng goa2 thak8 chiah-e5 oe7 e5 si5, u7 chit8-e5 pi2 chin-toa7 e5 lui5 khah thang kiaN-hiaN5 e5 siaN tui3 goa2 kong2: “Ki-ni5-hui (Chiniquy), kin-cha2-khi2 li2 kong2, Ma2-li7-a tui3 Ia5-sou kiu5 e5 long2 u7 tit-tioh8, li2 thoan5 peh8-chhat8 oe7. Li2 kiam2 bo5 khoaN3-tioh8 Ma2-li7-a lai5 kau3 Ia5-sou e5 bin7-cheng5 kiu5 beh kiN3 I, si7 in-ui7 Ia5-sou li7-khui i khi3 thoan5 hok-im kui2-na7 geh8-jit8, kam2-kak kou-toaN, sou2-i2 chiah siuN7 beh kiN3 i e5 kiaN2 mah? Ma2-li7-a lai5 kau3 Ia5-sou thoan5-to7 e5 sou2-chai7, in-ui7 lang5 chin choe7, ti3-kau3 boe7 thang jip8-khi3. I beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3? I beh eng7 i choe3 lau7-bu2 e5 te7-ui7 khi3 choe3. I chhut-siaN iau3-kiu5 Ia5-sou chhut-lai5 kiN3 i, chong2-si7 Ia5-sou thiaN-tioh8 I e5 lau7-bu2 e5 siaN, chiu7 eng7 I seng3 e5 bak8-chiu khoaN3 i, I u7 tah-eng3 i e5 chheng2-kiu5 bo5? I e5 hi7-khang ku7-choat8 i e5 siaN, I u7 ku7-choat8 i e5 ki5-kiu5. Chit pai2 si7 kong-khai e5 chek-pi7, hou7 i kam2-kak siuN7 kek8-liat8. Hiah-e5 lang5 long2 gong5-ngiah8. In ki5-koai3, chha-put-to beh siN khi2 hoan2-kam2. In ng3 Ki-tok ka7 I kong2: “Li2 chaiN2-iuN7 m7 lai5 kap li2 e5 lau7-bu2 kong2-oe7?” Ia5-sou chaiN2-iuN7 kong2? I bo5 in3 sim2-mih8, chi2-u7 kong2, “Sim2-mih8 lang5 si7 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2, sim2-mih8 lang5 si7 goa2 e5 hiaN-ti7?” Koh khoaN3 I e5 hak8-seng kong2: “KhoaN3-ah, goa2 e5 lau7-bu2, goa2 e5 hiaN-ti7 kap goa2 e5 chi2-be7.” Ma2-li7-a khia7 ti7 hia, bo5-heng5 tiong siu7 chek-pi7. 
  Au7-lai5 hit e5 siaN chhin-chhiuN7 lui5, tui3 goa2 kong2, kio3 goa2 tioh8 koh khah thak8 Ma2-kho2 3:31-35. Ti7 Ma2-kho2 kap Lou7-ka 8:19-21, li2 oe7 thang khoaN3-tioh8 siang7 chit8-iuN7 e5 su7-kiaN7. Ia5-sou put-tan3 bo5 tah-eng3 i e5 chheng2-kiu5, hoan2-tng2 eng7 chit8-chiong2 e5 in3-tap ti7 cheng3-lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 chi2-chek I e5 lau7-bu2.Au7-lai5 hit-e5 siaN koh eng7 thang kiaN-hiaN5 e5 koan5-ui tui3 goa2 kong2, Ia5-sou soe3-han3 e5 si5, u7 sun7-hok8 Iok-sek kap I e5 lau7-bu2; Chong2-si7 tng Ia5-sou eng7 Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2, se3-kan e5 Kiu3-chu2, jin5-lui7 choe3-toa7 e5 Kng e5 te7-ui7 lai5 piau2-hian7 ti7 se3-kan lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 e5 si5, Ma2-li7-a e5 chun5-chai7 chiu7 siau-biat8 khi3. Se3-kan lang5 e5 bak8-chiu chi2-u7 tioh8 chu3-sin5 khoaN3 Ia5-sou, lai5 chiap-siu7 I e5 Kng kap Oah8-mia5. 
  Peng5-iu2, hit e5 siaN thong-mi5 tui3 goa2 kong2: “Ki-ni5-kui! Ki-ni5-kui! Li2 kin-cha2-khi2 kong2 peh8-chhat8, li2 thoan5 chin choe7 bo5 i3-su3, ka-ki7 liap-cho7 e5 kou3-su7; Li2 kong2 Ma2-li7-a u7 koan5 thang tit-tioh8 i tui3 Ia5-sou sou2 kiu5 e5, si7 kap Seng3-keng siong-hoan2.” Goa2 thi5-khau3 ki5-to2, thong-mi5 khun3 boe7 khi3. 
  Keh cha2-khi2, Hu3-chu2-kau3 chhiaN2 goa2 khi3 kap i saN-kap chiah8 cha2-tng3. 
  I tui3 goa2 kong2: “Ki-ni5-kui, li2 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 thong-mi5 lau5 bak8-sai2 e5 khoan2, tau3-te2 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3?” 
  Goa2 kong2, “Chu2-kau3, si7 lah, goa2 e5 sim u7 boe7 thang heng5-iong5 e5 kou-toaN.” 
  “U7 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3?” I mng7. 
  “Ah! Goa2 boe7 thang ti7 chia ka7 li2 kong2.” Goa2 kong2: “Li2 m7-chai oe7 thang hou7 goa2 ka-ki7 chit8-e5 khi3 li2 e5 pang5-keng chit8-tiam2 cheng ku2 boe7? Goa2 beh chiong chit-e5 li2 sou2 giau5-gi5 e5 pi3-bit8 ka7 li2 kong2.” 
  Chiah8 cha2-tng3 liau2 au7, goa2 kap i saN-kap chhut-khi3, tui3 i kong2: 
  “Cha7-jit8, goa2 kong2 Ia5-sou siong5-siong5 un2-chun2 I e5 lau7-bu2 Ma2-li7-a e5 chheng2-kiu5. Li2 u7 toa7-toa7 o-lo2 goa2 e5 kang2-to7. Chong2-si7 Chu2-kau3, cha7-am3 goa2 u7 thiaN-tioh8 chit8-chiong2 pi2 li2 e5 siaN koh-khah toa7 e5 siaN-im, ia7 goa2 e5 bun7-toe5 chiu7-si7 in-ui7 goa2 sin3 hit-e5 siaN si7 siong7-te3 e5 siaN. Hit-e5 siaN tui3 goa2 kong2, lan2 chiah-e5 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 sin5-hu7 kap chu2-kau3, mui2-pai2 tui3 lan2 e5 kau3-iu2 thoan5 kong2, Ma2-li7-a si5-siong5 u7 koan5 thang tit-tioh8 Ia5-sou un2-chun2 i sou2 kiu5 e5, si7 hi-ke2. Chit-e5 si7 peh8-chhat8. Chu2-kau3, goa2 kiaN-liau2 chit e5 si7 kho2-oN3 koh si7 kek8-toa7 e5 chho3-gou7 lah.” 
  Chu2-kau3 kong2: “Ki-ni5-kui, li2 si7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3? Li2 si7 sin kau3-tou5 mah?” 
  “M7-si7” Goa2 kong2, “Goa2 m7-si7 sin kau3-tou5.” (Goa2 in-ui7 ai3 thak8 Seng3-keng, bat kui2-na7-pai3 hou7 lang5 chheng choe3 sin kau3-tou5.) “Goa2 tng-bin7 tui3 li2 kong2, goa2 sit8-chai7 chin kiaN-hiaN5, goa2 cha7-jit8 thoan5 peh8-chhat8 oe7. Chu2-kau3, li2 na7-si7 au7-pai2 ia7 thoan5 kong2, lan2 tioh8 tui3 Ma2-li7-a ki5-kiu5, in-ui7 Ia5-sou boe7-bat ku7-choat8 Ma2-li7-a tui3 I sou2 kiu5 e5, na7 an2-ni li2 ia7 si7 kong2 peh8-chhat8. Che-si7 hi-ke2 e5.” 
  Chu2-kau3 kong2: “Ki-ni5-kui, li2 siuN7 m7-tioh8 lah!” 
  “Bo5, Chu2-kau3,” Goa2 kong2: “Kan-ta kong2 si7 bo5 li7-ek, chia u7 Hok-im-su, chhiaN2 li2 thak8.” 
  Goa2 chiong Hok-im-su khng3 ti7 Chu2-kau3 e5 chhiu2, i chiu7 chiau3 goa2 sou2 in2-iong7 e5 chiuN-chat lai5 thak8. Ti7 goa2 e5 in2-siong7 tiong, goa2 kak-tit i thak8 chiah-e5 chiuN-chat si7 thau5 chit8-pai2. Chit e5 kho2-lin5 e5 lang5 hui-siong5 gong5-ngiah8, ti3-kau3 boe7-hiau2 kong2 oe7, chi2-u7 phih8-phih8-chhoah. Choe3-au7 i mng7 kong2: “Hit-e5 si7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3?” 
  “Ho2” goa2 kong2: “Che si7 Hok-im-su, tui3 an2-ni li2 oe7 thang chai, Ma2-li7-a lai5 tui3 Ia5-sou kiu5 e5 si5, I put-tan3 chek-pi7 i, ia7 bo5 liah8 i choe3 I e5 lau7-bu2. I ti7 kong-chiong3 e5 bin7-cheng5 an2-ni choe3, lan2 chiu7 oe7 thang chai Ma2-li7-a si7 Ia5-sou jiok8-the2 siong7 e5 lau7-bu2, m7-si7 sin5-leng5 siong7 e5 lau7-bu2.” 
  Chu2-kau3 gang7--khi3, m7-chai tioh8 choe3 sim2-mih8. I ia7 boe7 oe7 in3 goa2. 
